OL,3,C'I'm going to stab you': Rise in abuse
OL,4,Cof GP staff
OL,6,FStaff working in GP surgeries have
OL,7,Fspoken out about the racial abuse and
OL,8,Fphysical threats they face after
OL,9,Fstatistics revealed 95% of workers in
OL,10,FSouth Yorkshire had been targeted by
OL,11,Fpatients.
OL,13,FPrimary Care Sheffield (PCS), which
OL,14,Fsupports 75 GP practices in the city,
OL,15,Fhas launched a campaign to encourage
OL,16,Fkindness following a rise in incidents.
OL,18,FYvonne, a receptionist at one surgery
OL,19,Fin Sheffield, said: "I've had
OL,20,Fcolleagues that have been racially
OL,21,Fabused and things like that.
