OL,3,C'I'm going to stab you': Rise in abuse
OL,4,Cof GP staff
OL,6,F"But now they're getting threats -
OL,7,F'I'm going to do your car', 'I'm going
OL,8,Fto stab you', 'I'm going to throw this
OL,9,Fat you'.
OL,11,F"There have been surgeries where
OL,12,Fcomputers have been thrown in
OL,13,Freception, so it's definitely getting
OL,14,Fmore on the physical side."
OL,16,FFigures from PCS show that, in South
OL,17,FYorkshire, 95% of staff in GP
OL,18,Fsurgeries have experienced verbal
OL,19,Fabuse. More than half have faced
OL,20,Fintimidation and over a third have
OL,21,Fbeen threatened with physical violence.
