OL,3,C'I'm going to stab you': Rise in abuse
OL,4,Cof GP staff
OL,6,FOne in six have been attacked.
OL,8,FThe campaign, called Don't Leave A
OL,9,FGap, highlights the impact when staff
OL,10,Fhave to take time off work or resign
OL,11,Faltogether due to stress.
OL,13,FLiz, another receptionist in
OL,14,FSheffield, recently returned to work
OL,15,Fafter seven weeks off.
OL,17,F"You just put the phone down and
OL,18,F(think) I can't do this job any more.
OL,19,FThat's how it gets you," she said.
