OL,3,C'I'm going to stab you': Rise in abuse
OL,4,Cof GP staff
OL,6,F"It's just constant - the demands are
OL,7,Fthat high. You try to do your best and
OL,8,Fit's, it's not enough."
OL,10,FPCS medical director Dr Lucy Cormack
OL,11,Fsaid patients would experience the
OL,12,Fconsequences when staff struggle to
OL,13,Fcope.
OL,15,F"If you don't have staff in surgeries,
OL,16,Fthen people can't get access," she
OL,17,Fsaid "The phones don't get answered
OL,18,Fquickly enough, we reduce appointment
OL,19,Ftimes. It causes a huge knock on
OL,20,Fimpact to the rest of the service."
