OL,3,C'I'm going to stab you': Rise in abuse
OL,4,Cof GP staff
OL,6,FDoncaster GP Prof Vijay Kumar is a
OL,7,Fmember of the Royal College of GPs,
OL,8,Fwhich discussed rising abuse at a
OL,9,Frecent meeting.
OL,11,FHe said record waiting lists
OL,12,Fcontributed to patient frustration.
OL,14,F"Never in the history of NHS in my
OL,15,Fcareer have I come across this number
OL,16,Fwaiting," he said. "The frustration
OL,17,Fseems to be taken out against primary
OL,18,Fcare staff. Where else can patients
OL,19,Fturn?"
