OL,3,C'I'm going to stab you': Rise in abuse
OL,4,Cof GP staff
OL,6,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,7,Fsaid the problem was "unacceptable".
OL,9,FA spokesperson said: "GPs have our
OL,10,Ffull support in refusing to treat or
OL,11,Freporting to police abusive patients.
OL,13,F"Through our plan for change we are
OL,14,Fworking with GPs to reform primary
OL,15,Fcare, cut red tape and bring back the
OL,16,Ffamily doctor, and last week agreed a
OL,17,Fnew contract worth #13.2m."
